World Wide Web through standards set by the World Wide Web Consortium. The goal of the Semantic Web is to make Internet data machine-readable."]}],"equivalentConcepts":null}],"retrievalQueriesText":"PoolParty: The PoolParty Semantic Suite is a comprehensive middleware software. It includes a browser-based taxonomy management, thesaurus management, linked data, ontology management, corpus management, extraction and Semantic MiddleWare Configurator.\\nPoolParty Semantic Web skills\\nPoolParty product knowledge\\nPoolParty Skills","queryExpansion":{"broaderContext":[],"related":[],"examples":[],"synonyms":[],"categories":[],"primary":["PoolParty"]},"llmContextText":"# Knowledge Graph Context\\n\\nThe following concepts were extracted from the user's query and enriched with semantic relationships from our knowledge graph:\\n\\n**Understanding the Semantic Relationships:**\\n- **Preferred Label**: The main/official name for this concept\\n- **Alternative Labels**: Other names, synonyms, or ways this concept is commonly referred to\\n- **Definition**: Formal explanation of what this concept means\\n- **Scope Notes**: Usage guidance and contextual information about when to use this concept\\n- **Examples**: Concrete examples of how this concept is applied\\n- **Matched As**: The exact text from the user's query that triggered this concept\\n- **Confidence**: How confident we are this concept matches the user's intent (exact match = 100%, high = 80-99%, medium = 60-79%, low = <60%)\\n- **Broader Concepts**: More general/parent concepts that this concept belongs to (hierarchical relationship - \\"is-a\\" or \\"part-of\\")\\n- **Hierarchy Path**: Complete path from this concept to the root of the taxonomy\\n- **Categories**: The thematic classification or domain this concept belongs to\\n- **Related Concepts**: Associated concepts that are semantically connected but not hierarchical\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Extracted Concepts:\\n\\n### 1. PoolParty\\n**What it means:** The PoolParty Semantic Suite is a comprehensive middleware software. It includes a browser-based taxonomy management, thesaurus management, linked data, ontology management, corpus management, extraction and Semantic MiddleWare Configurator.\\n**Also known as:** PoolParty product knowledge\\n**Matched from query:** \\"PoolParty\\"\\n**Broader concepts (parent categories):**\\n  • Semantic Web skills (aka: Semantic Tech, Semantic technology)\\n    → The Semantic Web, sometimes known as Web 3.0, is an extension of the World Wide Web through standards set by the World Wide Web Consortium. The goal of the Semantic Web is to make Internet data machine-readable.\\n**Belongs to category:**\\n  • Skills\\n\\n---\\n\\n**How to use this context:**\\nUse the above semantic relationships to better understand what the user is asking about. The broader concepts show the hierarchical context, categories show the domain/topic area, and related concepts show connected ideas. The hierarchy path shows where this concept fits in the overall knowledge structure. When the confidence score is below 100%, consider that the match may be ambiguous and clarify with the user if needed.","keywordsText":"PoolParty, PoolParty product knowledge, Semantic Web skills, Skills","customPropertyDetails":{}},"executionId":"4143"},"question":"What is PoolParty?","conversationId":"410ad7ae-99f4-4119-9489-7d432e25e91e","internalN8nUrl":"http://n8n:5678","graphdb":{"grpahdbMCPresponse":""},"backendSseMessageUrl":"http://conversation-service:8080/sse/message","userId":"alice"},"jwtToken":"eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCIgOiAiSldUIiwia2lkIiA6ICJsMEJSWEJXV1dyNnVkRW85UXVPZWZNVDMyZ3RSd3c3dmJKaXJRNi1CWWtvIn0..ZM_KjP0N2M8NJc2avOAgjyCL6l7sruRKm0Yg_H07qeYy-L6LZPZqsqwlMIi5uHSqZqvVfsKeRkQz3Gca6Q-pZDA7zIC72aPb8ydHflAf8IcF1_UKn-cANDK2DXgZabVj3X6gZtfToXKYBG8GU8n6_taCgsJ4tR7lWfWa4BCg-m9uegPokJuSK8nvNVMDGXIWvUrcWC_q0eeUSjA4bD2L8Om_e7ahjK1sbWqBGGd_o6Hdx9xCsd7p0E7oTtFU51u_imvdD1JgbhYaeNk8WzufsPbz2liY3X4x_51FnEb1jQFIVqQfNhw2GJ4SHYdIRvdNMOI-xjaSDp1OvTcNP3-hYA","finalAnswer":"## What is PoolParty?\\n\\nPoolParty is a comprehensive semantic technology platform designed for managing taxonomies, thesauri, and knowledge organization systems. It serves as middleware software that enables organizations to create, manage, and leverage semantic data for various applications including content classification, search enhancement, and data integration.\\n\\n### Key Components and Features:\\n• **Taxonomy and Thesaurus Management**: Browser-based tools for creating and maintaining controlled vocabularies, concept schemes, and hierarchical knowledge structures\\n• **Project-Based Organization**: PoolParty projects serve as containers that can hold multiple concept schemes, top concepts, and related taxonomic information\\n• **Semantic Integration**: Supports automatic tagging, content classification through text mining, and synchronization with external systems like SharePoint\\n• **Multi-language Support**: Configurable language settings and user group management for international deployments\\n• **Authentication and Security**: Multiple authentication methods including password-based, single sign-on, social login, and multi-factor authentication with industry-standard security practices\\n\\n### Technical Architecture:\\nPoolParty Semantic Suite is built as a Java-based application running on Apache Tomcat 9, with a JavaScript-based frontend. The platform includes built-in graph databases (GraphDB or RDF4J) for managing semantic data, Apache Solr for entity extraction and search indexing, and Apache Spark for machine learning tasks. It also supports integration with external graph databases through its Semantic Middleware Configurator.\\n\\n### Business Applications:\\nThe platform enables organizations to implement faceted search, auto-complete functionality, and semantic search capabilities based on automatically tagged content. It's particularly valuable for content management, knowledge organization, and enhancing information discovery across enterprise systems.\\n\\n**References:**\\n* s3://graphwisekh/helpTxt96_flattened/6575a5cd38__poolparty-project.html.txt\\n* s3://graphwisekh/helpTxt96_flattened/130b22f5b3__poolparty-system-architecture.html.txt\\n* s3://graphwisekh/helpTxt96_flattened/f3e05c9ee3__is-there-a-sharepoint-integration-with-poolparty-.html.txt\\n* s3://graphwisekh/helpTxt96_flattened/e086d6995d__information-security-practices-and-procedures.html.txt\\n* s3://graphwisekh/helpTxt96_flattened/otkg (1).part5443.ttl"}}]}	13c61bee-52a6-435c-a13e-e9605068dd45	0	k_QWKVPcxAcK31dGK641t	{"instanceId":"982a83c4fa14b8860ea8391b8f766ad449d7431aac64126d0b9fc936877b58be"}	\N	f	9	\N	13c61bee-52a6-435c-a13e-e9605068dd45	[]
